window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>For Mage Alex Verus, everything is on the line in the 10th urban fantasy novel from the nationally best-selling author of </b><b><i>Marked</i></b><b>.</b></p> <p>Once, Alex Verus was a diviner trying to live quietly under the radar. Now, he's a member of the Light Council who's found success, friends...and love. But it's come with a price - the Council is investigating him, and if they find out the truth, he'll lose everything.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Alex's old master, Richard Drakh, is waging a war against the Council, and he's preparing a move that will bring Alex and the life mage, Anne, under his control. Caught between Richard and the Council, Alex's time is running out. To protect those he cares for, Alex will have to become something different. Something darker....</p>"; 
